00122 bool CompositeOFMultiply::evaluate_with_gradient( EvalType type, 
00123                                              PatchData& pd,
00124                                              double& value_out,
00125                                              std::vector<Vector3D>& grad_out,
00126                                              MsqError& err )
00127 {
00128   double value_2;
00129   bool ok;
00130   
00131   ok = objFunc1->evaluate_with_gradient( type, pd, value_out, grad_out, err );
00132   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !ok) return false;
00133   ok = objFunc2->evaluate_with_gradient( type, pd, value_2, mGradient, err );
00134   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !ok) return false;
00135   
00136   assert( grad_out.size() == pd.num_free_vertices() );
00137   assert( mGradient.size() == pd.num_free_vertices() );
00138   
00139   std::vector<Vector3D>::iterator i = grad_out.begin(), j = mGradient.begin();
00140   while (i != grad_out.end()) {
00141     *i *= value_2;
00142     *j *= value_out;
00143     *i += *j;
00144     ++i;
00145     ++j;
00146   }
00147   value_out *= value_2;
00148   return true;
00149 }

00151 bool CompositeOFMultiply::evaluate_with_Hessian_diagonal( EvalType type, 
00152                                             PatchData& pd,
00153                                             double& value_out,
00154                                             std::vector<Vector3D>& grad_out,
00155                                             std::vector<SymMatrix3D>& diag_out,
00156                                             MsqError& err )
00157 {
00158   double value_2;
00159   bool valid;
00160 
00161   valid = objFunc1->evaluate_with_Hessian_diagonal( type, pd, value_out, grad_out, diag_out, err );
00162   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !valid) return false;
00163   valid = objFunc2->evaluate_with_Hessian_diagonal( type, pd, value_2, mGradient, mDiagonal, err );
00164   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !valid) return false;
00165 
00166   for (size_t i = 0; i < pd.num_free_vertices(); ++i) {
00167     diag_out[i] *= value_2;
00168     mDiagonal[i] *= value_out;
00169     diag_out[i] += mDiagonal[i];
00170     diag_out[i] += outer_plus_transpose( grad_out[i], mGradient[i] );
00171 
00172     grad_out[i] *= value_2;
00173     mGradient[i] *= value_out;
00174     grad_out[i] += mGradient[i];
00175   }
00176   
00177   value_out *= value_2;
00178   return true;
